flowchart LR
    SVC[Service]

    SVC --> METRICS[metrics: Prometheus]
    SVC --> LOGS[logs: structured JSON]
    SVC --> TRACES[traces: OTLP]

    METRICS --> DASH[Grafana dashboards]
    LOGS --> AGG[log aggregator]
    TRACES --> JAEGER[Jaeger / Tempo]

    DASH --> SLO{SLO breach?}
    SLO -->|no| OK[all green]
    SLO -->|warn| PAGE[PagerDuty alert]
    PAGE --> ONCALL[on-call engineer]
    ONCALL --> RUNBOOK[runbook lookup]
